<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Subscription Cancelled</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #6c757d; color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Subscription Cancelled</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>We're sorry to see you go. Your subscription for <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has been cancelled.</p>

    <div style="background-color: #fff; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Your data will be retained for 30 days until <strong>{{dataRemovalDate}}</strong>.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
        After this date, all your photographs, rolls, collections, and account data will be permanently deleted.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Changed your mind?</strong></p>
    <p>You can resubscribe at any time before {{dataRemovalDate}} to keep all your data.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{resubscribeUrl}}" style="background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
        Resubscribe
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
      Thank you for being part of Only35. We hope to see you again!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>This is an automated message from Only35.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
